# RoboLedger V5.2.19: High-Fidelity Functional Audit

A comprehensive structural and functional upgrade to the V5 interface, bringing it to "Stock Market" levels of dynamic polish while resolving deep-seated parsing and performance issues.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Sequential Ref# System**: I am enabling dynamic Ref# re-sequencing. This means the Ref# (e.g., 001) will always prioritize the top-most row in the current view, updating live as you sort or filter. 
> **Flicker-Free Navigation**: I am switching the Account Switcher from a full-page re-render to a Tabulator-native filter. This will eliminate flickering and hangs, but requires the grid to be fully initialized with all data at once.
> **Adaptive Account Naming**: Switches from `CHQ` -> `CHQ` to a smarter `CHQ1` | `CHQ2` logic with chronological sorting (AMEX -> MC -> CHQ).

## Proposed Changes

### UI Logic (app.js)
- **Scale Expansion**: Increase all `max-width: 1060px` instances to **`1166px`** (+10%).
- **Static Render Prevention**: Re-wire `window.render()` and the Account Switcher to use `txnTable.setFilter()` for account isolation. This prevents the "screen flick" and hanging.
- **Adaptive Naming**: Implement a type-aware label generator for the switcher pills.
- **Pagination**: 
  - Enable Tabulator `pagination: "local"`.
  - Add a footer controls bar with page-size limit dropdown and navigation arrows.
- **Settings Persistence**: Fix [toggleSettings()](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js#514-520) and the save logic to ensure theme (Rainbow default) and density choices are saved to `UI_STATE`.

### Styling (system.css)
- **Structural Dividers**: Add vertical `1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06)` lines to grid headers.
- **Dynamic Sorting**: Enable native CSS transitions for Tabulator row movement.
- **Rainbow Default**: Set the Purple-to-Cyan rainbow header as the default theme.
- **COA Tags**: Implement high-fidelity CSS for COA tags (`.coa-tag`) to support the "tickers" update effect.

### Core Logic (ledger.core.js)
- **Parser Polarity Audit**: 
  - Fix `Ingestion.processUpload` to correctly distinguish between debits and credits based on row sign and column headers.
  - Implement a check for negative values in the "Amount" field to correctly set `Polarity.DEBIT`.
- **Sequential Indexing**: Ensure the ledger engine supports live position-based indexing for the Ref# column.

### Session Persistence (V5.2.20)
- **Recovery Logic**: Implement a check in [init()](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/ledger.core.js#553-556). If transactions exist in `window.RoboLedger.Ledger.getAll()`, set `UI_STATE.recoveryPending = true`.
- **In-Page Recovery UX**: Add a sleek, V5-styled banner to the top of the `v5-unified-island-wrapper` (above the header card).
  - **Continue**: Dismisses banner and keeps existing data.
  - **Start New**: Triggers `Ledger.reset()`, refreshes the view.

### Forensic Audit Drawer (V5.2.21)
- **Architecture**: Implement a right-side full-height sidebar (`.audit-drawer`) that compresses the main stage when active.
- **Embedded Viewer**: 
  - **PDF**: Load `sourceFileBlob` into an `<iframe>` for forensic verification.
  - **CSV**: Implement a lightweight grid preview for non-binary sources.
- **Contextual Sync**: Wire [openSourceFile(fileId)](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js#187-217) to toggle the drawer and update the viewer without page reloads.
- **UI Interaction**: clicking the "Source" icon in the grid (e.g., RBC, CHQ1) opens the side-by-side view.

### Logic Wiring & Metadata Fidelity (V5.2.23)
- **Search Engine**:
  - Implement `window.toggleSearch()` and `UI_STATE.isSearchOpen`.
  - Add search input in the action bar with Tabulator `setFilter` integration for live "Search-as-you-type".
- **Ref# Refresh Logic**:
  - Consolidate duplicate [handleRefUpdate](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js#1483-1496) functions.
  - Ensure [render()](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js#39-44) is called after a ref update to instantly refresh account switcher pills.
- **Metadata Canonical Alignment**:
  - Fix property mismatch (`account_num` vs `accountNumber`) in [renderTransactionsRestored](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js#909-1064).
  - Ensure Transit#, Institution#, and Account# are accurately displayed for the active account.

### Grid Header & COA Fidelity (V5.2.24)
- **Header Structure**:
  - Sharpen header dividers to `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6)` for better visibility against the rainbow.
  - Add a subtle `1px` right border to the body cells (`rgba(0,0,0,0.1)`) to align with headers.
- **Truncation Fixes**:
  - Increase `Ref#` width to **`90px`**.
  - Increase [Source](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js#187-217) width to **`85px`**.
  - Increase `Debit/Credit` widths to **`110px`**.
- **COA Editor Restoration**:
  - Switch from `editor: "list"` to `editor: "select"` with robust value mapping.
  - Ensure the editor correctly captures and displays the [COA](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js#951-987) dropdown by default.
  - Wire the selection to update the transaction's `coa_code`.
- **Visual Polish**:
  - Apply `letter-spacing: 0.02em` and `font-size: 10.5px` to header titles for a "Wall Street" look.
  - Fix header sorting arrow overlap by adjusting title padding.

### Forensic Recon Hub & Metadata Intelligence (V5.2.25)
- **Universal Recon Hub**:
  - Implement a reconciliation UI on the right side of the Switcher Bar.
  - Logic for **Asset Accounts** (CHQ/SAV): `Opening - Debit + Credit = Ending`.
  - Logic for **Liability Accounts** (VISA/MC/AMEX): `Opening + Debit - Credit = Ending`.
  - Provide a native editable box for the "Opening Number".
- **Enhanced CC Metadata**:
  - Implement IIN logic to detect specific card brands (VISA: 4xxx, MC: 5xxx, AMEX: 3xxx).
  - Extract and display 15 (AMEX) or 16 (VISA/MC) digit account numbers from statements.
  - Display full branding in metadata (e.g., "RBC AVION VISA").
- **View-Dependent Metadata**:
  - `ALL` view -> Display "ALL LEDGERS".
  - Specific Account -> Display detailed Transit/Inst/ACC# or Card Info.
- **Ingestion Routing Fix**:
  - Ensure `account_id === 'ALL'` during upload is resolved to the primary account ledger.

### Grid Header Fidelity (V5.2.24)
- **Header Structure**:
  - Sharpen header dividers to `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6)` for better visibility against the rainbow.
  - Add a subtle `1px` right border to the body cells (`rgba(0,0,0,0.12)`) to align with the header.
- **Truncation Fixes**:
  - Increase [Source](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/ui/enterprise/app.js#187-217) column width to **`85px`**.
  - Increase `Debit/Credit` column widths to **`110px`**.
  - Ensure `tabulator-col-title` has horizontal padding to prevent arrow overlap.
- **Visual Polish**:
  - Apply `letter-spacing: 0.02em` and `font-size: 10.5px` to header titles for a "Wall Street" look.
  - Align sorting arrows to the right of the title with a fixed gap.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Verification
- **Stress Test**: Switch between accounts rapidly with 1000+ transactions to verify no flicker.
- **Parser Test**: Import a mixed-polarity statement and verify Debit/Credit column distribution.

### Manual Verification
- Verify that "ALL" view shows the combined ledger correctly.
- Confirm Ref# 001 moves to the new top row after a Date sort.
